{
  "stem": "8370.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I explained him, well, I am finishing 21 today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never expected to-- he say, OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am sorry for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He walked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After a minute, he arrived with a birthday gift.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the most beautiful birthday gift in my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me half a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I will remember to the end of my days this half loaf of bread for my 21st birthday.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had couple of barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was two where they had really shelves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a-- how do you call it in English-- [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, there was a little bit some blankets on which they have been put in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a very, very difficult and very horrible condition, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You saw sometime, there are photograph from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was lucky, because I was, due to the fact that I was working as a [? health ?] doctor, I was on duty attached to the block number 12.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And block number 12 was, I would say, a VIP block.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was three-story beds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was better condition there, a little better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But of course, there was no civilized condition, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Forget about it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Especially, there was no medicine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Mengele, who was in charge of the hospital medical service that was all Auschwitz, arrived from time to time and checked.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He never approached the patient in the bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He checked only the card of the patient hanging outside the bed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If it was written [? grippe, ?] which mean flu, with question mark, he realized very quick that it is a typhoid.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And everybody, doesn't matter it was a Jew or Polish or Russian or French, once you got typhoid, the black fever, was put to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
